Title: Cupid & Psycho
Plot: Allegations against the Strike Team are front-page news, and the team is broken up pending the investigation.  Mackey threatens to reveal that Officer Lowe is gay if he won't recant his statement about the Strike Team.  In the meantime, Vic and Claudette find themselves following the trail of a batch of ""cupid"" meth, while Shane and Dutch try to get along on a case.
ParentalRatingReason: R16 Violence,offensive language,drug use and sex scenes
GuestStars: John Diehl, Brent Roam, Derek Hamilton, Efrain Figueroa, K.K. Dodds, Johnny Whitworth, Dick Anthony Williams, Jamie Anderson, Christopher Neiman
